    ID: "1010",
    Title: "How to make the most out of your internship",
    Content:
      '<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><div align="center" style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-align: center; text-indent: -.25in;"></div><div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bBhpr2QYGv0/V3Rq7sVtX_I/AAAAAAAAU_c/YO8KODnxYhE2rtiPBfSC9RRuz-iWXg6KACKgB/s1600/Intern-Thumb.jpg" style="clear: right; display: inline !important; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="208" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bBhpr2QYGv0/V3Rq7sVtX_I/AAAAAAAAU_c/YO8KODnxYhE2rtiPBfSC9RRuz-iWXg6KACKgB/s320/Intern-Thumb.jpg" width="320" /></a></div><div style="text-indent: -24px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;If you\'re interning this summer, this video is a &nbsp;must-watch. Internships are an exciting time<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;for students and future employees. Make sure to make the most out of your time at the company you\'re interning at. Here\'s what to do to have a successful time there:</div><ol><li><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%; text-indent: -0.25in;"><span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</span></span><span dir="LTR" style="text-indent: -0.25in;"></span><span style="line-height: 115%; text-indent: -0.25in;">Act as if you were hired and working for the company</span></li><li><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%; text-indent: -0.25in;"><span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</span></span><span dir="LTR" style="text-indent: -0.25in;"></span><span style="line-height: 115%; text-indent: -0.25in;">Always have a professional attitude and attire</span></li><li><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;"><span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</span></span><span dir="LTR" style="text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;"></span><span style="line-height: 115%; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;">Be prepared to take on work and ask for work/ offer help</span></li><li><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;"><span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</span></span><span dir="LTR" style="text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;"></span><span style="line-height: 115%; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;">Communicate well</span></li><li><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;"><span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</span></span><span dir="LTR" style="text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;"></span><span style="line-height: 115%; text-align: left; text-indent: -0.25in;">Network</span></li></ol><br /><div><span style="line-height: 115%;">Benefits to doing a great internship:</span></div><div><span style="line-height: 115%;"><br /></span></div><div style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%;">·<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%;">You leave great impressions<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%;">·<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%;">You will get great recommendations<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%;">·<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%;">You will make long-lasting connections<o:p></o:p></span></div><div style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%;">·<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%;">You may be able to get a job offer <o:p></o:p></span></div><div style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: &quot;symbol&quot;; line-height: 115%;">·<span style="font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%;">You will learn what you need to learn</span></div><div style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="line-height: 115%;"><br /></span></div><div style="margin-left: .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">To watch the video, click here:&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 18.4px;">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mx8DGo7NOJM</span></div><div><br /></div><div><o:p>Good luck with your internship and have a happy summer!!</o:p></div><div><o:p><br /></o:p></div><div><b>DISCLAIMER:</b> Sorry about the noise in the video!</div><div><br /></div><div>Please comment, share and let\'s stay in touch!&nbsp;</div><div><br /></div><div>Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/safaanhairy/</div><div>Twitter: https://twitter.com/safaanhairy</div><div>Instagram: http://instagram.com/safaanhairy</div><div><o:p></o:p></div><div>My blog: http://safaanhairy.blogspot.com/</div></div>',
