    Content:
      '<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><div><div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><iframe width="320" height="266" data-thumbnail-src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/yR5ArrtUREg/0.jpg" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yR5ArrtUREg?feature=player_embedded" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>December is 31 days of opportunity to change habits and get closer to your goals<o:p></o:p></div><div><br /></div><div>Experts say that habits can get developed if done sustainable 21 days successively. So you still got a chance!!<o:p></o:p></div><div><br /></div><div><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yR5ArrtUREg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">In this video</a>, I give you 5 tips, I use myself, to catch up on my goals list and make the most out of december.</div><div><br /></div><div>Think of that feeling of satisfaction you\'d get at the end of the month/year when you\'d feel your time wasn\'t waited ;)</div><div><br /></div><div>This challenge is for all of us and I hope it\'ll help us get ahead.</div><div><br /></div><div>Good luck to us all and comment below if you have other tips to share.</div><div><br /></div><div><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yR5ArrtUREg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CLICK HERE TO WATCH THE VIDEO</a></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div></div>',
