    ID: "1047",
    Title: "My Favorite Quotes",
    Content:
      '<div dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Hello there</span><br /><div style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-uWFMIX29Hvo/U8aP7TbxuEI/AAAAAAAASPw/2ikPCBUIRGs/s1600/8799060-beautiful-butterfly-28350.jpg" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-uWFMIX29Hvo/U8aP7TbxuEI/AAAAAAAASPw/2ikPCBUIRGs/s1600/8799060-beautiful-butterfly-28350.jpg" height="200" width="320" /></a></div><span style="font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><br /></span><span style="font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">I have decided to post all the quotes I have been scribbling on different pieces of paper that I&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">have read or heard and that caught my attention. They are from authors, motivational speakers, artists etc. I find reading them over and over helps me stick them in my mind and make me do better every day. I hope it\'ll help you too. This page will be updated on a regular basis.&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><br /></span><span style="font-family: Helvetica Neue, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Happy reading :)</span><br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;****************<br /><br />Life is not about me. It\'s about we.<br /><br />What you get never makes you happy long-term. What you become makes you very happy or very sad.<br /><br />Ask and you shall receive.<br /><br />A no-limit person will never say \'I don\'t have enough\'.<br /><br />Life will pay whatever price you ask for.<br /><br />I want more money. Fine here\'s a buck and get out of here.<br /><br />There is no way to happiness. Happiness is the way.<br /><br />A no-limit person celebrates lessons in life.<br /><br />You\'ll see it when you\'ll believe it.<br /><br />If you\'re not doing what you love and loving what you do, you have two choices : a. Change what you\'re doing, b. Change how you feel about what you\'re doing.<br /><br />Good morning God or Good God! morning<br /><br />Become independent of the good opinion of other people.<br /><br /><br /><b>If you have a favorite quote, please share it below. Thanks.</b><br /><br /><br /></div>',
    Excerpt: "",
