    Title:
      "How to Build a Business Around Your Passion 2019 | Inspiring Story of a Coach, Teacher & Author",
    Content:
      'I am very passionate about helping people build a business around their passions. I have done it myself and other people around me have too. And it\'s possible for you too.<a href="https://youtu.be/OdyYb0jqLFY"><img src="https://safaanhairy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Build-a-business-around-your-passion-300x169.png" alt="" width="369" height="208" class="wp-image-1351  alignright"></a>\n\nIn my <a href="https://safaanhairy.com/2019/04/29/how-to-build-a-business-around-your-passion-2019-inspiring-story-of-a-coach-teacher-author/">last video</a>, I told you about the things you need to know before you consider starting a business. In <a href="https://youtu.be/OdyYb0jqLFY">this video</a>, I am interviewing Zineb Nassrou, an entrepreneur, coach &amp; author, who shares her journey and what led her to quit her job, travel the world and start a business.\n\nEntrepreneurship is not an easy road but it\'s definitely one of the most rewarding ones. You just need to be armed with patience and willingness to do the work strategically.\n\nFind out about <a href="https://youtu.be/OdyYb0jqLFY">Zineb\'s story</a> and the steps she undertook to turn her passion into a profitable business.\n\n<strong><em>Don\'t forget to comment, like the video and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7kdlVV0AcfNCFB6olaVPjA?&amp;ab_channel=SafaaNhairy">subscribe</a> to my channel.</em></strong>',
