    ID: "1508",
    Title: "Number One Mistake People Who Want to Succeed Make",
    Content:
      '<a href="https://youtu.be/yU5Llpp_qas"><img src="https://safaanhairy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Mistake-1-300x169.png" alt="" width="378" height="213" class=" wp-image-1510 alignright" /></a>Everybody wants to succeed but in my life as an entrepreneur and educator, I see so many people making one mistake repeatedly. Yet, this is probably the most crucial thing to do if you want to experience and enjoy success in your life.\r\n\r\nMost people take wonderful resolutions and start taking action. But just when things begin to get hard, they do this common thing: quit too soon. They throw in the towel saying they did everything they could to make it work and that it may not be the right decision to go with. While it may be true, for most people, it is actually just the beginning of the beginning. When things get hard, it is a sign that you are doing something right. You are going that extra mile other people are going willing to take.\r\n\r\nWhen you face roadblocks, challenges, obstacles, the thing NOT to do is to quit. This is the first filter you will have to go through and only patient and worthy people shall remain. So do NOT QUIT.\r\n\r\nAnother big mistake, I talk about in the <a href="https://youtu.be/yU5Llpp_qas">video</a>, is that most people are desiring and wanting what other people have. The problem with this is that other people\'s goals may not be yours. This is why it is so IMPORTANT to check in with yourself, connect with your inner self and chase goals your heart is truly wanting. If you are pursuing goals that belong to other people, you will not succeed because your heart is not in them.\r\n\r\nWatch the <a href="https://youtu.be/yU5Llpp_qas">video</a> for more.\r\n\r\n<strong>COMMENT DOWN BELOW AND LET ME KNOW WHAT IS THE BEGINNING THING SABOTAGING YOUR SUCCESS AT THE MOMENT</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;',
