      '<p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://safaanhairy.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Protect-your-business-300x169.png" alt="" width="300" height="169" class="size-medium wp-image-1513 alignright">Whether it comes to insurance or law, most of us tend to think of protection only after a problem has occurred. When you are building a business, no matter how big or small it is, it is smart to protect your work, creations and genius. In this <a href="https://youtu.be/wkAQiNNMEtM">interview</a>, intellectual property specialist, Celeste Reumert, explains the 5 things you need to be aware of as a business owner and what to do to protect your business from potential intellectual theft.</p>\nWatch the <a href="https://youtu.be/wkAQiNNMEtM">video</a> and let us know what part of your business will you protect next.\n\n&nbsp;',
